Line 8x8-inch pan with foil. Grease foil with shortening. Cover bottom of pan with grahams. Microwave caramel bits and milk in a bowl for 2 minutes on HIGH, stirring every 30 seconds until melted. Pour over grahams. Top with peanuts, marshmallows, crushed pretzels and chocolate. Refrigerate at least 1 hour. Use foil to remove dessert from pan before cutting into bars to serve.